mysql_groundtruth: SELECT EMPLOYEE_ID, DEPARTMENT_ID FROM EMPLOYEE GROUP BY EMPLOYEE_ID HAVING COUNT(*) = 1 UNION SELECT EMPLOYEE_ID, DEPARTMENT_ID FROM EMPLOYEE WHERE PRIMARY_FLAG = 'Y'
SELECT e.employee_id, e.department_id FROM employee e WHERE e.primary_flag = 'Y' OR e.employee_id IN (SELECT employee_id FROM employee GROUP BY employee_id HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT department_id) = 1);
